{&quot;leader&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:0,&quot;point&quot;:&quot;0.5in&quot;}]" data-list-id="4" data-list-info="{&quot;id&quot;:4,&quot;l&quot;:0}">De bewoning van de woning</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class="zw-list zw-paragraph" data-tabpoints="[{&quot;leader&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:0,&quot;point&quot;:&quot;0.5in&quot;}]" data-textformat="{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Carlito,Calibri&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(33,37,41)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:12,&quot;fw_i&quot;:300}" data-margin-left="0.25in" data-text-indent="-0.25in" data-padding-left="0.25in" data-margin-bottom="14pt" data-margin-top="14pt" data-tab-info="[{&quot;leader&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:0,&quot;point&quot;:&quot;0.5in&quot;}]" data-list-id="4" data-list-info="{&quot;id&quot;:4,&quot;l&quot;:0}">De waardeontwikkeling van de woning</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class="zw-list zw-paragraph" data-tabpoints="[{&quot;leader&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:0,&quot;point&quot;:&quot;0.5in&quot;}]" data-textformat="{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Carlito,Calibri&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(33,37,41)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:12,&quot;fw_i&quot;:300}" data-margin-left="0.25in" data-text-indent="-0.25in" data-padding-left="0.25in" data-margin-bottom="14pt" data-margin-top="14pt" data-tab-info="[{&quot;leader&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:0,&quot;point&quot;:&quot;0.5in&quot;}]" data-list-id="4" data-list-info="{&quot;id&quot;:4,&quot;l&quot;:0}">Veranderingen in de schenkingsvrijstelling</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class="zw-paragraph" data-textformat="{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Carlito,Calibri&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(33,37,41)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:12,&quot;fw_i&quot;:300}" data-margin-bottom="14pt">Wanneer u of uw partner de woning verlaten, koopt Thuisborg, of een andere door Thuisborg aangewezen partij, uw woning. Mocht u komen te overlijden gedurende de periode van bewoning na verkoop, dan zullen alle resterende bedragen waar u zelf recht op heeft, door Thuisborg worden doorbetaald aan uw erfgenamen.</p>\n<p class="zw-paragraph" data-textformat="{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Carlito,Calibri&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(33,37,41)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:12,&quot;fw_i&quot;:300}" data-margin-bottom="14pt">Houd u nog recht op periodieke uitkeringen van de woningopbrengst?</p>\n<ul data-list-id="5" data-list-format="{&quot;level5&quot;:{&quot;paraFormat&quot;:{&quot;ti&quot;:&quot;-0.25in&quot;,&quot;tps&quot;:[{&quot;leader&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:0,&quot;point&quot;:&quot;3.0in&quot;}],&quot;pl&quot;:&quot;0.25in&quot;,&quot;ml&quot;:&quot;2.75in&quot;,&quot;textFormat&quot;:{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Wingdings&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:10}},&quot;c&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:8,&quot;ltype&quot;:23,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level4&quot;:{&quot;paraFormat&quot;:{&quot;ti&quot;:&quot;-0.25in&quot;,&quot;tps&quot;:[{&quot;leader&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:0,&quot;point&quot;:&quot;2.5in&quot;}],&quot;pl&quot;:&quot;0.25in&quot;,&quot;ml&quot;:&quot;2.25in&quot;,&quot;textFormat&quot;:{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Wingdings&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:10}},&quot;c&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:7,&quot;ltype&quot;:23,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level7&quot;:{&quot;paraFormat&quot;:{&quot;ti&quot;:&quot;-0.25in&quot;,&quot;tps&quot;:[{&quot;leader&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:0,&quot;point&quot;:&quot;4.0in&quot;}],&quot;pl&quot;:&quot;0.25in&quot;,&quot;ml&quot;:&quot;3.75in&quot;,&quot;textFormat&quot;:{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Wingdings&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:10}},&quot;c&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:7,&quot;ltype&quot;:23,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level6&quot;:{&quot;paraFormat&quot;:{&quot;ti&quot;:&quot;-0.25in&quot;,&quot;tps&quot;:[{&quot;leader&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:0,&quot;point&quot;:&quot;3.5in&quot;}],&quot;pl&quot;:&quot;0.25in&